In [24]:
def annual_risk_return(stock_rets):
    tradeoff = stock_rets.agg(["mean", "std"]).T
    tradeoff.columns = ["Return", "Risk"]
    tradeoff.Return = tradeoff.Return*252
    tradeoff.Risk = tradeoff.Risk * np.sqrt(252)
    return tradeoff
